OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FM&S pulls Christmas ad post
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter 'flag' backlash      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, M&S has apologised after being accused 
OL,6, of posting an Instagram photo of       
OL,7, Christmas party hats in the colours of 
OL,8, the Palestinian flag on fire.          
OL,10,FThe image, an out-take from one of the 
OL,11,Fcompany's TV adverts, showed red, green
OL,12,Fand silver hats burning in a fireplace.
OL,14,FM&S said the intent was to "playfully  
OL,15,Fshow that some people don't enjoy      
OL,16,Fwearing paper Christmas hats".         
OL,18,FThe company removed the photo and said 
OL,19,Fthe advert was filmed in August, before
OL,20,Fthe latest Israel-Gaza conflict began. 
